{"name":"兆麻","nameCn":"兆麻","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/d8/b1/22820_crt_mRRsR.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>兆麻</li><li><span>别名: </span>兆麻</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>かずま</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Kazuma</li><li><span>性别: </span>男</li>","detail":"神器型态：耳饰<br />毘沙门的神器。名为“兆”。戴着眼镜的青年。称呼毘沙门为“毘娜（ヴィーナ）”。是毘沙门神器当中最为古老的神器、“麻”之一族唯一存活下来的人。神器形状为樱花造型的耳环。本身的战斗能力低，负责指挥各个神器使他们的能力技术发挥到最大值（修正命中精度、攻撃范围的辅佐等），在毘沙门神器中担任最为重要的角色。他正确的引导被认为是“毘沙门成为最强武神的原因”，连夜斗也甘拜下风。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/105612","name":"『ノラガミ』キャラクターソングCD2","nameCn":"","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/77/ee/105612_0cEof.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/129988","name":"ノラガミ ARAGOTO","nameCn":"野良神 ARAGOTO","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/c6/07/129988_0fO7p.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"福山潤","castHref":"/person/3818","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/bf/00/3818_prsn_t0vDV.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/82572","name":"ノラガミ","nameCn":"野良神","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/ee/de/82572_PNW44.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"福山潤","castHref":"/person/3818","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/bf/00/3818_prsn_t0vDV.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/31426","name":"ノラガミ","nameCn":"野良神","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/69/b7/31426_eYx8o.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/84864","name":"ノラガミ OAD","nameCn":"野良神 OAD","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/f5/bb/84864_N8Y2B.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"福山潤","castHref":"/person/3818","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/bf/00/3818_prsn_t0vDV.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/147364","name":"ノラガミ ARAGOTO OAD","nameCn":"野良神 ARAGOTO OAD","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/e0/9c/147364_HO3hG.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"福山潤","castHref":"/person/3818","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/bf/00/3818_prsn_t0vDV.jpg"}]}